		"CHEF_DESCRIPTION": "A survivor of high class, romron gramsay specializes in only the most exquisite meals and combos. As a culinary master, romron gramsay uses a variety of practiced skills in tandem for additional benefits.<style=cSub>\n\n< ! > Dice throws a spinning cleaver that lingers in the air. Release Dice's skill button again to recall them, dealing damage on the return trip.\n\n< ! > Roll into enemies to close the distance, you can’t give a nice Sear from far away. Sear oiled enemies for a much stronger roast. \n\n< ! > Extra oil is sometimes needed to handle bigger meals. Oil can be spread across Petrichor V, allowing you to cook your enemies or freeze them for leftovers!\n</style>\n",
